    <lb n="1"/>Δημάριν καὶ Εἰρήνη Σύρῳ τῶι φιλ-

    <lb n="2"/>τάτῳ πλεῖστα χαίρειν. 

    <lb n="3"/>οἴδα<add place="supralinear">μεν</add> ὅτι ἀηδῶς <choice><corr>ἔχεις</corr><sic>εχις</sic></choice> <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">διὰ</unclear> <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">τ</unclear>ὴν <choice><corr>λειψυδρί-

    <lb n="4"/>αν</corr><sic>λιψυδριαν</sic></choice>, τοῦτο οὐ μόνον <choice><corr>ἡμῖν</corr><sic>ημειν</sic></choice> γενάμενον 

    <lb n="5"/>ἀλλὰ καὶ πολλοῖς, <choice><corr>ἐπ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ισ</supplied>τάμεναι</corr><sic>επ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ισ</supplied>ταμενοι</sic></choice> <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ὅ</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">τ</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ι</unclear> <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ο</unclear>ὐδ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ὲν</unclear> 

    <lb n="6"/>παρὰ σὲ γέγονε. καὶ νῦν ἐπιστάμεθά σου 

    <lb n="7"/>τὸ σπουδαῖον <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">κα</unclear>ὶ ὡς ἐπίκεισαι τοῖς ἔργοις 

    <lb n="8"/>τοῦ κλήρου, <choice><corr>ἐλπίζουσαι</corr><sic>ελπιζοντες</sic></choice> σὺν θεῷ τὸ <choice><corr>πε-

    <lb n="9"/>δίον</corr><sic>πεδειον</sic></choice> σπαρῆναι. ὅσα ποτὲ οὖν ἐὰ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ν</unclear> <choice><corr>ἀνα-

    <lb n="10"/>λώσῃς</corr><sic>αναναλωσης</sic></choice> <choice><corr>εἰς</corr><sic>ις</sic></choice> τὴν τοῦ κλήρου κατεργασίαν, 

    <lb n="11"/><choice><corr>ἡμῖν</corr><sic>ημειν</sic></choice> ἐνλόγησον ἐπὶ λόγου. δέξαι παρὰ 

    <lb n="12"/>Νιννάρου <choice><corr>εἰς</corr><sic>ις</sic></choice> λόγον Εἰρήνης τὸ ἐπιβάλλον 

    <lb n="13"/>αὐτῇ μέρος καὶ <choice><corr>εἰς</corr><sic>ις</sic></choice> τὸ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ν</supplied> λόγον Δημαρίου ὁ-

    <lb n="14"/>μοίως δέξαι πα<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ρ</supplied>ὰ <supplied cert="high" reason="lost">Ἁτ</supplied>ρῆτος τὸ ἐπιβάλλον 

    <lb n="15"/>αὐτῇ μέρος. ἐρρῶσθ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">α</supplied>ί σε εὐχόμεθα. 
</ab></div><div n="v" part="N" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="16"/><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">Σύρῳ παρὰ </supplied><choice><corr><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">Εἰρή</supplied>νης</corr><sic><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ειρη</supplied><g type="x"/>νης</sic></choice> καὶ Δημαρίου. </ab></div></div><div n="meta.27907" part="N" type="description"><p><rs cert="high" type="material">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.27907" part="N" subtype="textDate" type="commentary"><p><date notAfter="200" notBefore="101" type="textDate">II</date></p></div><div n="meta.27907" part="N" subtype="principalEdition" type="bibliography"><listBibl><bibl subtype="principal" type="publication"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Ryl.</title><biblScope type="volume">2</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">243</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos"><biblScope type="numbers">27907</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP"><series>0198</series>; <biblScope type="volume">2</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">243</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" href="0198;2;243" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO" type="Perseus">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.27907" part="N" subtype="illustrations" type="bibliography"><p>keine</p></div><div n="meta.27907" part="N" subtype="translations" type="bibliography"><head>Übersetzungen</head><listBibl lang="en"><head lang="de">Englisch:</head><bibl type="translations">Bagnall - Cribiore, Women's Letters (2006), S. 350</bibl><bibl type="translations">Bagnall - Cribiore, Women's Letters (2008), B5.5, Nr. 243</bibl></listBibl></div><div n="meta.27907" part="N" subtype="locations" type="history"><p>unbekannt</p></div><div n="meta.27907" part="N" type="figure"><p><figure href="http://enriqueta.man.ac.uk:8081/BrowserInsight/BrowserInsight?cmd=start&amp;un=uman&amp;pw=est1824=&amp;cid=ManchesterDev-93-NA&amp;iia=0&amp;ig=Rylands%20Papyri&amp;isl=0&amp;gwisp=0%7CReference_number%7CReference%20number%7C1%7CGreek%20Papyrus%20243%7C1&amp;gwia=3&amp;gc=0"><figDesc